snippet.title: Amber Heard NOT Being Investigated by LAPD For Perjury! | What a MESS!
snippet.description:
Amber Heard's attorney claims there is no truth to reports that she is being investigated for perjury by the Los Angeles Police Department in connection to an alleged physical altercation with former husband Johnny Depp, Radar can exclusively report.
